works.title: Vuedex
works.fadeText: This is a Pokdex developed in Vue.js for a technical challenge.
works.body: The project was developed with Vue 3 and Vite, and has some features like Vue Test Utils for testing, search, filter by type, name or specie, infinite scroll, and has support for multiple languages.
